description.en:
After all these increases, the cosmic price booms. Our beloved dog has become a sweet fat man. But is there anything to stop him? Will the dog manage to take one more bite? Will Elon continue to pamper his pet?
Welcome to a new network, a great community, we're going to do our best to bring out the best from Fat Doge to spread the world. Being the No.1 meme token in Ethereum is our goal.
